<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA6">
<l>vāṉattā ṉeṉpāru meṉkamaṟ ṟumparkōṉ</l>
<l>ṟāṉattā ṉeṉpārun tāmeṉka - ñāṉattāṉ</l>
<l>muṉṉañcat tāliruṇṭa meyyoḷicēr kaṇṭattā</l>
<l>ṉeṉṉeñcat tāṉeṉpaṉ yāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>All those who say “the divine one”, let them say so. Then again, all those who say</l>
<l>“he from the realm of the king of those beyond”, let them say so.</l>
<l>“He with knowledge, he with a throat with true light darkened by the poison,</l>
<l>he in my heart”, say I.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
